MOVIE TICKET BOOKING PROJECT - WORK FLOW OF THE PROJECT 

====================================================
1. APPLICATION ENTRY FLOW
====================================================

main.jsx
  -> App.jsx
      -> AppContext.jsx
          -> Clerk Authentication
          -> Axios Requests
          -> Admin State
          -> Favorites State
          -> Shows Data

====================================================
2. FRONTEND ROUTING FLOW
====================================================

App.jsx
│
├── /
│   └── Home.jsx
│       ├── HeroSection.jsx
│       ├── FeaturedSection.jsx
│       ├── TrailersSection.jsx
│       └── MoviesCard.jsx
│
├── /movies
│   └── Movies.jsx
│
├── /movies/:id
│   └── MovieDetails.jsx
│       └── DateSelect.jsx
│           └── navigate('/movies/:id/:date')
│
├── /movies/:id/:date
│   └── Seatlayout.jsx
│
├── /my-bookings
│   └── MyBookings.jsx
│
├── /favorites
│   └── Favorites.jsx
│
├── /recommendation
│   └── Theaters.jsx
│
└── /admin/*
    ├── Dashboard.jsx
    ├── AddShows.jsx
    ├── ListShows.jsx
    └── ListBookings.jsx

====================================================
3. SERVER STARTUP FLOW
====================================================

server.js
│
├── connectDB()
├── clerkMiddleware()
├── Stripe Webhook Route
├── Inngest Route
├── showRouter
├── bookingRouter
├── adminRouter
├── userRouter
└── recommendationRouter

====================================================
4. AUTHENTICATION FLOW
====================================================

User Login
    ↓
Clerk
    ↓
getToken()
    ↓
Axios Header
    ↓
Authorization: Bearer TOKEN
    ↓
Backend
    ↓
clerkMiddleware()
    ↓
req.auth()

====================================================
5. ADMIN FLOW
====================================================

Admin Page
    ↓
GET /api/admin/is-admin
    ↓
protectAdmin()
    ↓
Clerk User Lookup
    ↓
Role Check
    ↓
isAdmin()

Dashboard
    ↓
GET /api/admin/dashboard
    ↓
getDashboardData()
    ↓
Booking Model
    ↓
Show Model
    ↓
User Model
    ↓
Dashboard Statistics

====================================================
6. MOVIE BOOKING FLOW
====================================================

Home.jsx
    ↓
MovieDetails.jsx
    ↓
DateSelect.jsx
    ↓
Book Now
    ↓
Seatlayout.jsx
    ↓
Select Seats
    ↓
POST /api/booking/create
    ↓
createBooking()
    ↓
Booking Model
    ↓
MongoDB

====================================================
7. PAYMENT FLOW
====================================================

Seatlayout.jsx
    ↓
Create Booking
    ↓
Stripe Checkout Session
    ↓
Stripe Payment Page
    ↓
User Pays
    ↓
Stripe Webhook
    ↓
stripeWebhooks.js
    ↓
booking.isPaid = true
    ↓
Inngest Event
    ↓
Confirmation Email

====================================================
8. INNGEST FLOW
====================================================

Booking Created
    ↓
app/checkpayment
    ↓
releaseSeatsAndDeleteBooking()
    ↓
Sleep 10 Minutes
    ↓
Booking.findById()
    ↓
isPaid ?

YES
 └── Keep Booking

NO
 ├── Show.findById()
 ├── Release occupiedSeats
 ├── show.save()
 └── Delete Booking

====================================================
9. USER SYNC FLOW
====================================================

Clerk User Created
    ↓
webhook-integration/user.created
    ↓
syncUserCreation()
    ↓
User.create()

Clerk User Updated
    ↓
webhook-integration/user.updated
    ↓
syncUserUpdate()
    ↓
User.findByIdAndUpdate()

Clerk User Deleted
    ↓
webhook-integration/user.deleted
    ↓
syncUserDeletion()
    ↓
User.findByIdAndDelete()

====================================================
10. RECOMMENDATION SYSTEM FLOW
====================================================

Theaters.jsx
    ↓
/api/recommendations/search
    ↓
recommendationController.js
    ↓
Python Recommendation API
    ↓
Movie Suggestions

Selected Movie
    ↓
/api/recommendations
    ↓
Python Model
    ↓
Recommended Movies
    ↓
TMDB API
    ↓
Poster + Overview
    ↓
Frontend

====================================================
11. DATABASE RELATIONSHIPS
====================================================

User
│
├── has many Bookings
├── has Favorites
└── has Time Tracking

Booking
│
├── belongs to User
├── belongs to Show
└── stores Payment Status

Show
│
├── belongs to Movie
├── has occupiedSeats
└── has showDateTime

Movie
│
└── has many Shows

====================================================
12. ROUTER TO CONTROLLER MAP
====================================================

showRouter
│
├── /now-playing -> getNowPlayingMovies
├── /add -> addShow
├── /all -> getShows
└── /:movieId -> getShow

bookingRouter
│
├── /create -> createBooking
└── /seats/:showId -> getOccupiedSeats

adminRouter
│
├── /is-admin -> isAdmin
├── /dashboard -> getDashboardData
├── /all-shows -> getAllShows
├── /all-bookings -> getAllBookings
└── /all-users -> getAllUsers

userRouter
│
├── /sync -> syncCurrentUser
├── /track-time -> trackUserTime
├── /bookings -> getUserBookings
├── /update-favorite -> UpdateFavorite
└── /favorites -> getFavorites

recommendationRouter
│
├── /search -> searchRecommendationMovies
└── / -> getMovieRecommendations

